To simplify \(\bigl(\tfrac{5m}{n}\bigr)^{3}\), raise numerator and denominator to the third power:

\[
\bigl(\tfrac{5m}{n}\bigr)^{3}
= \frac{(5m)^{3}}{n^{3}}
= \frac{5^{3}\,m^{3}}{n^{3}}
= \frac{125\,m^{3}}{n^{3}}\quad(n\neq0).
\]

